@startuml fig-dhcp-dora
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam shadowing false
title DHCP DORA Process

participant "Client\n(no IP)" as C
participant "DHCP Server\n192.168.1.1" as S

C -> S : D: Discover (broadcast)\nSrc: 0.0.0.0 Dst: 255.255.255.255
S --> C : O: Offer\nIP: 192.168.1.100 Lease: 86400s
C -> S : R: Request (broadcast)\nRequesting 192.168.1.100
S --> C : A: Acknowledge\nAssigned, lease confirmed

legend right
Port 67 (server), 68 (client)
DHCP provides: IP, mask
gateway, DNS, lease time
tcpdump port 67 or 68
endlegend
@enduml
